    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine runs roughly and shows several noticeable fluid leaks, while the transmission exhibits harsh shifting between gears. The exterior has multiple dents and clear coat failure, and the interior shows heavy wear and tear. It is recommended for a buyer who is comfortable with a major project or needs a parts car.",
      "price": 3800.0,
